Sentencas: A new type of Ruddlesden-Popper Pr1.2Sr0.8Ni1-xMoxO4+delta (PSNMO) cathode with x = 0, 0.025, 0.050, 0.075 was prepared by the sol-gel method.
Titulo: Mo doped Ruddlesden-Popper Pr1.2Sr0.8NiO4+δ oxide as a novel cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The conductivity of Pr1.2Sr0.8NiO4+delta cathodes reaches the max values and then decreases the continuous increase of Mo amount in all the Mo doped cathodes.
Titulo: Mo doped Ruddlesden-Popper Pr1.2Sr0.8NiO4+δ oxide as a novel cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Results of elec-trochemical impedance spectroscopy show that the Pr1.2Sr0.8Ni0.950Mo0.050O4+delta has the lowest polarization resistance of 0.110 Omega cm2 at 750 degrees C among PSNMO cathodes.
Titulo: Mo doped Ruddlesden-Popper Pr1.2Sr0.8NiO4+δ oxide as a novel cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: And results of electrical conductivity relaxation and X-ray photoelectron spectroscopy indicate that Mo-doping improves the oxygen surface exchange properties of PSNMO cathodes, which can be mainly ascribed to co-interaction of oxygen vacancy and interstitial oxygen in PSNO cathodes after Mo-doping.(c) 2022 Elsevier B.V.
